desc: Lycoming County's premier mobile outfitter! Kayaks, Canoes, Stand-Up Paddle Boards, River Tubes, Bikes, and E-Bike Rentals! Guided Tours and Instruction! Delivery and Shuttle service. Check out our selection of swag and outdoor gear! Four convenient retail locations. Call 570-692-2537 for more information!

layout.text: Board, Paddle, Bike, & Hike. We got everything you need to experience the PA Wilds like never before. Full service bike, skate, outdoor gear shop, and mobile outfitter! Kayak, stand up paddle board, tube, and bike rentals!
